          <ul>
            <li><strong>Open Vector Stores:</strong> Let's create a vector store. Switch to the <em>Chat</em> tab and click <em>Vector Stores</em>.</li>
            <li><strong>Provide a document to ingest:</strong> Use a Pre-Authenticated Request (PAR) link to let Studio fetch your source document from Object Storage.</li>
            <li><strong>Create the vector store:</strong> Studio ingests the document, chunks it, generates embeddings, and stores everything in your database so you can query it with <code>DISTANCE()</code> and <code>ML_RAG()</code>.</li>
          </ul>

